<p><strong><?php _e('You can customize the display of this screen in a number of ways:', 'promotion-slider'); ?></strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><?php _e('You can hide/display columns based on your needs and decide how many promotions to list per screen using the Screen Options tab.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
	<li><?php _e('You can filter the list of promotions by status using the text links in the upper left to show All, Published, Draft, or Trashed posts. The default view is to show all promotions.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
	<li><?php _e('You can view promotions in a simple title list or with an excerpt. Choose the view you prefer by clicking on the icons at the top of the list on the right.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
	<li><?php _e('You can refine the list to show only promotions in a specific category or from a specific month by using the dropdown menus above the promotions list. Click the Filter button after making your selection. You also can refine the list by clicking on the promotion author or category in the promotions list.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
</ul>

<p><strong><?php _e('Hovering over a row in the promotions list will display action links that allow you to manage your promotion. You can perform the following actions:', 'promotion-slider'); ?></strong></p>

<ul>
	<li><?php _e('Edit takes you to the editing screen for that promotion. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the promotion title.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
	<li><?php _e('Quick Edit provides inline access to the metadata of your promotion, allowing you to update promotion details without leaving this screen.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
	<li><?php _e('Trash removes your promotion from this list and places it in the trash, from which you can permanently delete it.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
	<li><?php _e("Preview will show you what your draft promotion will look like if you publish it. View will take you to your live site to view the post. Which link is available depends on your promotion's status.", 'promotion-slider'); ?></li>
</ul>

<p><strong><?php _e('You can also edit multiple promotions at once.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></strong> <?php _e('Select the promotions you want to edit using the checkboxes, select Edit from the Bulk Actions menu and click Apply. You will be able to change the metadata (categories, author, etc.) for all selected promotions at once. To remove a promotion from the grouping, just click the x next to its name in the Bulk Edit area that appears.', 'promotion-slider'); ?></p>

